<ptxt>KEY REMINDER WARNING SYSTEM DESCRIPTION</ptxt>
<step2>
<ptxt>When the driver's side door is opened with the ignition key in the ACC or LOCK position, this system causes a buzzer to sound in order to warn the driver that the ignition key has not been removed.</ptxt>
